    <rigor-reason>Production code change in `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Capabilities/CapabilityRouter.cs` (routing decisions affect cost / correctness); FULL rigor + Step 9.5 quality gates mandatory</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>P2-W1</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Disjoint file (`CapabilityRouter.cs`) vs Wave 1 peers (CitationExtractor, AnalysisChatContextResolver, UploadEndpoints)</parallel-reason>
    <production-fix-per-ledger>true</production-fix-per-ledger>
